irc-chatter (0.1.90) unreleased; urgency=low

  * IRC library updated to newest version
  * IRC library is now embedded into the app
  * Support for sending raw commands to the server
  * Support for sending CTCP requests
  * Up/Down buttons work in the text entry field
  * Channel names are now sorted
  * Clicking on a username will now query the user
  * Automatic reconnect when the connection is lost
  * Font size setting now works
  * TODO: Support for connecting to multiple servers at the same time
  * TODO: Some adjustments to the user interface

 -- Timur Kristóf <venemo@msn.com>  Sun, 04 Dec 2011 13:48:22 +0200

irc-chatter (0.1.1) unstable; urgency=low

  * Some small optimalizations
  * Message view deletes the last 100 messages if there are more than 300
  * Support for setting server port
  * Support for connecting with SSL
  * Now using applauncherd for boosting startup time
  * Added splash screens for both portrait and landscape
  * License changed to GPLv2+

 -- Timur Kristóf <venemo@msn.com>  Sun, 14 Aug 2011 22:41:22 +0200

